Class AmpCaching

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.module.aim.util.caching.AmpCaching

  • public class AmpCaching
extends java.lang.Object
    various caching stuff. Only cache seldomly-changing data here
    They are put together in a class to be easy to find out what to invalidate in case some global stuff changes
